# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.0] - 2019-08-24
### Added
- GearVR & Carboard support
- Toggle support
- Dropdown support
- Slider support
- Scrollbar support
- MIT Licence

### Changed
- Optimized update loop
- Exemple scene is updated with all compatible UI elements
- Modern reticle animations

## [0.1] - 2016-10-11
### Added
- Exemple scene
- Button support
- Slider support (with steps)
- Exemple video : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8U4ChekAgnQ